"2018-10-01T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"電競唔係運動？手指運動黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc527b0c094f87e178e427c953e425c939d97832","tid":843264,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b0e8fa16aadb3ef4e33a773a581afe571f54cd0","tid":843264,"uid":155723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"廢老文"},{"pid":"bb79ae40556de832c86ef386e9b2c3322f3ca46b","tid":843264,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"算啦,比個希望d鍾意打機既廢青同毒撚啦<br />\n無謂踩到咁盡"},{"pid":"ceddd44149dcc79908d48d80dd125045eed8788f","tid":843264,"uid":56743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"同強國家級既運動員，過氣就食屎。"},{"pid":"7f483807e1ce21a5b5dbb7a40fa3c0d6ec119611","tid":843264,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6db835144dea54ec4a3d4ac3b137c9d487deaf","tid":843264,"uid":154579,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"其實講咁多都係市場供需啫，拗黎拗去又有咩意思。<br />\n<br />\n打機電競又好, 傳統運動又好, 本質上都係無實質上既生產, 而係娛樂觀眾既產業。多人睇 &rarr; 多廣告, 贊助 &rarr; 收入。講咩 &quot;<em>「電競運動員」不似真正的運動員，當中少數人一時的高薪，無疑只是背後商家樂意支付的廣告費</em>&quot;, 兩樣都係架啦, 佢到底知唔知市場點運作架。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔反對電競, 不過我贊同的確唔少學生只係讀書唔好諗住可以靠打機, 根本無考慮過係對自己人生既博奕。如果真係想走職業, 佢地有無好似準職業運動員同樣既覺悟? <br />\n<br />\n不過呢潘國林講咩 &quot;不要讓運動會淪為電競商漁利的工具&quot;, 運動會本身就係商業活動黎架啦, 佢呢個年紀仲咁天真?"},{"pid":"fd2bc2867cb4b134a6597735e0fc7df286f49e6c","tid":843264,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"又踩中連登毒撚電競手條尾"},{"pid":"31ee713fe1850db36b611935b755ecc48c357079","tid":843264,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55701995c3fde1cb0ad3094133fb8934e9d5c32a","tid":843264,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32fd70dfd7319663780e22dda25578284a7313a6","tid":843264,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef88344674b0f1b5f7e5e646b7a092885ee3804d","tid":843264,"uid":3807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"將打鼓機同跳舞機歸納為電競<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"但打鼓機同跳舞機點解唔可以係電競？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"依家D電競選手，企1分鐘都攰啦，點玩跳舞機啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:04:16.000Z","msg":"咁係個 D 人廢，跳舞機唔係電競冇關係"},{"pid":"45e2f902f41ec47eb32f9ed06881661ae0af0ecf","tid":843264,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87b4090cdebb7fa67e2e9c72d3e61f0c408c444f","tid":843264,"uid":77633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32fd70dfd7319663780e22dda25578284a7313a6","tid":843264,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef88344674b0f1b5f7e5e646b7a092885ee3804d","tid":843264,"uid":3807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"將打鼓機同跳舞機歸納為電競<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"但打鼓機同跳舞機點解唔可以係電競？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"街機音樂game 其實一早已經有比賽啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"所以唔明點解唔可以電競<br />\n班傻鳩比商家佬洗腦，覺得指定遊戲先叫電競"},{"pid":"6e2b57563989c51d0e8349a8de24d214de8fdb5b","tid":843264,"uid":57488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"文匯都貼<br />\non9"}]}